### Retrieve Supabase Auth Session (v2 vs v1) with Async API

Source: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/www/_blog/2022-08-16-supabase-js-v2.mdx

Compares the new asynchronous `supabase.auth.getSession()` in `supabase-js` v2 with the synchronous `supabase.auth.session()` in v1. This update resolves race conditions for token refreshing across multiple tabs by ensuring the library waits for a valid session before proceeding, improving stability.

```typescript
// v2
const { data } = await supabase.auth.getSession()
```

```typescript
// v1
const { data } = supabase.auth.session()
```

