### Sign out user from Supabase Auth session

Source: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/docs/content/guides/auth/social-login/auth-twitch.mdx

Removes the authenticated user from the browser session and clears any stored authentication objects from localStorage. This method handles cleanup of all session data across JavaScript, Flutter, and Kotlin platforms. Returns an error object if the sign-out operation fails.

```javascript
import { createClient } from '@supabase/supabase-js'
const supabase = createClient('<your-project-url>', '<sb_publishable_... or anon key>')

async function signOut() {
  const { error } = await supabase.auth.signOut()
}
```

```dart
Future<void> signOut() async {
  await supabase.auth.signOut();
}
```

