### Get user's current session (Dart)

Source: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/docs/docs/ref/dart/v0/upgrade-guide.mdx

Demonstrates how to retrieve the current authentication session in Dart. The 'Before' method accesses `supabase.auth.session()`, while the 'After' version uses the `supabase.auth.currentSession` property. The `currentSession` property returns a `Session?` object.

